node.text:
Award-winner Tankoa S501 hybrid M/Y Bintador, 50-meter of pure elegance is now on her 
way to the 2021 @monacoyachtshow_official ! The dynamic and contemporary exterior 
design by Francesco Paszkowski features large and comfortable outdoor entertainment 
spaces on each deck and a touch-and-go helipad.
.
. 
. @paszkowskidesign @names_byfrancescorogantin @margherita.casprini

This year they are worth 500€ ! Join the most exclusive and influential event of the year! 

Instructions to participate: follow @genoasuperyachthub, @theyachtmogul @onboardwithmarcela, and comment why are you a yachting fan, and tag three friends u wanna go with!

📸 @yvangrubski
